This is great, thank you so much for providing the documents.

I will see if I can upload and annotate the documents before our =
session, if not then I will upload and annotate right before 2pm.

One additional step I will need to take during the session to ensure it =
is legally binding is to confirm verbally yours and Muhoro's fiduciary =
roles as Trustee and Executor.

This is done with a simple affirmative statement confirmation I will =
perform during the session you will see below in the questions I=E2=80=99v=
e provided.=20

If you want to take it a step further you may provide a certificate of =
trust or trust agreement excerpt to confirm your roles, as per Florida =
Statutes, Section 736.1017 =
<https://www.flsenate.gov/laws/statutes/2020/736.1017>

Thank you for everything and I will see you and Muhoro at 2pm. If you =
need to reschedule for any reason please let me know and I will take =
care of it.
Questions for James Bey (Executor of JUSTIN JAMES ANDERSON ESTATE)

Identity Verification
"Please present a government-issued photo ID, such as a passport, you =
used for biometric verification. Can you confirm that the name on this =
ID is James Bey, and that you are the same individual signing as =
Executor of the JUSTIN JAMES ANDERSON ESTATE?"
Fiduciary Role Confirmation
"Do you confirm that you are signing these documents, including the =
Security Agreement and UCC-3 Amendment, in your capacity as Executor of =
the JUSTIN JAMES ANDERSON ESTATE, and that you are authorized to act in =
this role?"
Voluntary Intent
"Are you executing these documents voluntarily, without any coercion, =
duress, or undue influence from any party?"
Understanding of Document
"Do you acknowledge that you are signing the Security Agreement and =
related documents for the purposes stated therein, and that I, as a =
notary, am not providing legal advice or verifying the truthfulness or =
legality of the contents?"
Questions for Muhoro Francis (Trustee of Nova Persona Express Trust)

Identity Verification
"Please present a government-issued photo ID, such as a passport, you =
used for biometric verification. Can you confirm that the name on this =
ID is Muhoro Francis, and that you are the same individual signing as =
Trustee of the Nova Persona Express Trust?"
Fiduciary Role Confirmation
"Do you confirm that you are signing these documents, including the =
Security Agreement, Affidavit of Commercial Bonding, Payment Instruction =
Notice, Bonded Bill of Exchange, and other attached filings, in your =
capacity as Trustee of the Nova Persona Express Trust, and that you are =
authorized to act in this role?"
Voluntary Intent
"Are you executing these documents voluntarily, without any coercion, =
duress, or undue influence from any party?"
Understanding of Document
"Do you acknowledge that you are signing the Security Agreement, =
Affidavit, Payment Instruction Notice, Bonded Bill of Exchange, and =
related documents for the purposes stated therein, and that I, as a =
notary, am not providing legal advice or verifying the truthfulness or =
legality of the contents?"

